<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Xpora Adventure</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .header img {
            width: 150px;
        }
        .welcome {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .welcome h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .welcome p {
            color: #555;
        }
        .tour-highlights {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .tour-highlights h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .tour-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .tour-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .tour-item h3 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .tour-item p {
            color: #555;
        }
        .buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .buttons a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 5px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .btn-book {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }
        .btn-explore {
            background-color: #007bff;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #888;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .buttons a {
                padding: 10px;
                margin: 5px 0;
                display: block;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://your-logo-url.com/logo.png" alt="Xpora Adventure Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="welcome">
            <h1>Welcome to Xpora Adventure!</h1>
            <p>Your gateway to unforgettable experiences. Book your next adventure with us and explore the world like never before.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tour-highlights">
            <h2>Upcoming Tours</h2>
            <div class="tour-item">
                <img src="https://your-image-url.com/tour1.jpg" alt="Tour 1">
                <h3>Tour to the Majestic Mountains</h3>
                <p>Join us for an exhilarating trek through the stunning mountain ranges. An adventure awaits!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tour-item">
                <img src="https://your-image-url.com/tour2.jpg" alt="Tour 2">
                <h3>Explore the Enchanted Forests</h3>
                <p>Discover the mysteries of the forest with our guided tours. Perfect for nature lovers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="https://your-booking-url.com" class="btn-book">Book Now</a>
            <a href="https://your-website-url.com" class="btn-explore">Explore More</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Xpora Adventure. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
